+ * @axi_clk:		Handle to input clock 's_axi_aclk'
+ * @clks_internal:	Internal clocks
+ * @clkout:		Output clocks
+ * @suspended:		Flag indicating power state of the device
+ * @is_versal:		Flag indicating if it versal device
+ */
